島 ",{"type":33,"tag":56,"props":218,"children":220},{"href":219},"https://www.technice.com.tw/techmanage/infosecurity/99791/",[221],{"type":39,"value":222},"雲端專業需求大爆發 資安就業市場轉變中",{"type":39,"value":224},", 2024/03/07",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":226,"children":227},{},[228,230,236],{"type":39,"value":229},"產業人力供需資訊網 ",{"type":33,"tag":56,"props":231,"children":233},{"href":232},"https://theme.ndc.gov.tw/manpower/cp.aspx?n=C9ECDD0E995DB66B",[234],{"type":39,"value":235},"雲端服務暨巨量資料產業",{"type":39,"value":237},", 2024/04/19",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":239,"children":240},{},[241,242,246],{"type":39,"value":193},{"type":33,"tag":56,"props":243,"children":244},{"href":196},[245],{"type":39,"value":199},{"type":39,"value":201},{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250,252,258],{"type":39,"value":251},"Coursera ",{"type":33,"tag":56,"props":253,"children":255},{"href":254},"https://www.coursera.org/articles/cloud-security-engineer",[256],{"type":39,"value":257},"How to Become a Cloud Security Engineer: 2024 Career Guide",{"type":39,"value":259},", 2023/11/18",{"type":33,"tag":151,"props":261,"children":262},{},[],{"type":33,"tag":41,"props":264,"children":266},{"id":265},"人力市場需求",[267],{"type":39,"value":265},{"type":33,"tag":269,"props":270,"children":271},"p",{},[272],{"type":39,"value":273},"根據 1111 人力銀行資料庫顯示，目前網站上的工作機會數達到 67.4 萬筆，其中數位人才的工作機會數有將近 6 萬筆，而需求成長最快速的雲端人才，過去一年工作機會數增加了 19%，儼然是產業界的當紅炸子雞。",{"type":33,"tag":269,"props":275,"children":276},{},[277],{"type":39,"value":278},"雲端架構師這個職位雖然聽起來很帥，好像比工程師更厲害，但其實本質就是工程師，只是工作內容更加廣泛。一個工程師可能會專注在系統建置（系統工程師）、網路管理（網路工程師）、資料處理（資料工程師），而雲端架構師則同時會涵蓋到網路、系統、資料、權限和效能等領域。此外你面對的不是只有系統，還會常和客戶討論需求、對客戶教育訓練、做各種 POC、售後技術支援、擔任研討會講師以及撰寫部落格文章。",{"type":33,"tag":269,"props":280,"children":281},{},[282],{"type":39,"value":283},"身為一名雲端架構師，要具備的除了基本的資訊技術能力，還要能「把產品介紹清楚」（表達能力）、「 了解客戶需求」（系統分析能力） 、「 提供解決方案」（問題解決能力）、「了解各產業和各項產品功能」（學習能力）和「系統設定」（實作能力） 。",{"type":33,"tag":41,"props":285,"children":287},{"id":286},"cloud-security-engineer-certification",[288],{"type":39,"value":289},"Cloud Security Engineer Certification",{"type":33,"tag":269,"props":291,"children":292},{},[293],{"type":39,"value":294},"Five common certifications and certificates for cloud security engineers:",{"type":33,"tag":48,"props":296,"children":297},{},[298,309,319,329,339],{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":299,"children":300},{},[301,307],{"type":33,"tag":302,"props":303,"children":304},"strong",{},[305],{"type":39,"value":306},"Certified Information Systems Security Professional (CISSP)",{"type":39,"value":308}," is a globally recognized certification that verifies your IT security technical skills, and is often a standard for security professionals.",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":310,"children":311},{},[312,317],{"type":33,"tag":302,"props":313,"children":314},{},[315],{"type":39,"value":316},"AWS Certified Security",{"type":39,"value":318}," - Specialty validates your understanding of data classifications and AWS data protection mechanisms. This may be helpful for those who work in an AWS cloud architecture, networking, database, or in a related area.",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":320,"children":321},{},[322,327],{"type":33,"tag":302,"props":323,"children":324},{},[325],{"type":39,"value":326},"Google Cloud Professional Cloud Security",{"type":39,"value":328}," Engineer is a certificate that assesses your ability to ensure data protection, manage operations within a Google Cloud Platform environment, and more.",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":330,"children":331},{},[332,337],{"type":33,"tag":302,"props":333,"children":334},{},[335],{"type":39,"value":336},"Certificate of Cloud Security Knowledge (CCSK)",{"type":39,"value":338}," provides you with knowledge on cloud security programs and best practices.",{"type":33,"tag":52,"props":340,"children":341},{},[342,347],{"type":33,"tag":302,"props":343,"children":344},{},[345],{"type":39,"value":346},"Certified Cloud Security Professional (CCSP)",{"type":39,"value":348}," demonstrates to employers yo